+## Design Decisions
+
+| Decision | Rationale |
+|----------|-----------|
+| Single workflow file | Small codebase; one file is easier to audit than a split matrix |
+| Parallel jobs | Faster feedback; lint and security are independent of test execution |
+| Ruff over flake8 | Single tool covers both linting and formatting; 10–100× faster |
+| Bandit | Standard Python security scanner; B310 suppressed with `# nosec` for localhost urlopen calls which are intentional here |
+| No Docker | stdlib-only Python on `ubuntu-latest`; container overhead is not yet justified |
+| 80% coverage threshold | Signals intent; test job passes with 0 tests (no files exist yet) |
+
